---
title: Beef, Bacon & Rosemary Fettuccine for Dinner with Mediterranean Beef Couscous for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Whip up a hearty beef ragu with fettuccine for dinner, then an easy yet flavour-packed beef couscous bowl for lunch. Extra delicious!

